{
  "title": "Short Course Collection",
  "body": "<html><body><div id=\"block-ti-west-content\">\n<article>\n<div>\n<div>\n\n<div class=\"hero__container hero__container--black_overlay_left\" data-hero-container=\"\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<div class=\"hero__text-inset\">\n<div class=\"container__grid container__grid--2col\">\n<div class=\"hero__text-container none\">\n<h1 class=\"u-margin-hug u-font-family-secondary hero__title montserratbold\">Short Course Collection</h1>\n<p class=\"u-font-family-primary hero__sub-title\">Time-saving, cost-effective courses and Micro-Certs quickly sharpen your skills</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div>\n<section>\n<div class=\"container container--max-width\">\n<article class=\"container__grid media-block__container media-block__container--reversed\">\n<div class=\"media-block__img-container\">\n<img alt=\"A young African American woman in a suit and wearing her hair in braids in a bun works on an iPad in a brightly lit station while waiting for her train.\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2022-08/A%26B_ShortCourse1.jpg?itok=DO5D05Qr\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned/public/2022-08/A%26B_ShortCourse1.jpg?itok=DO5D05Qr 1x, /sites/default/files/styles/right_aligned_2x/public/2022-08/A%26B_ShortCourse1.jpg?itok=HLSCEwng  2x\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__header\">\n<hr aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"hr hr--offset hr--md hr--md--offset hr--light\" role=\"presentation\"/>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"media-block__content\">\n<p>Add to your skillset with on-demand courses and Micro-Certs designed for busy professionals like you that won’t eat up your free-time or weekends. Complete assignment modules in as little as 5 minutes, or a whole assignment in as little 25 minutes. Explore our courses and Micro-Certs today.</p>\n</div>\n\n</article>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n</div>\n<div> <div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--steps paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--steps-card paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<svg class=\"u-icon-arrows-clock-flat-dims\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#arrows-clock-flat\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div class=\"steps-label\">25 Minutes a Day</div>\n<div>Each online program features modules you can complete in as little as 5 minutes, or a whole assignment in as little 25 minutes.</div>\n<div class=\"arrow-right\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-arrow-right\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#arrow-right\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--steps-card paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<svg class=\"u-icon-online-learning-dims\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#online-learning\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div class=\"steps-label\">On-Demand</div>\n<div>Complete modules and assignments when and where you want with on-demand courses and Micro-Certs.</div>\n<div class=\"arrow-right\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-arrow-right\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#arrow-right\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--steps-card paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<svg class=\"u-icon-stopwatch-flat-dims\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#stopwatch-flat\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div class=\"steps-label\">Self-Paced</div>\n<div>Set your own schedule, complete assignment modules in as little as 5 minutes, or a whole assignment in as little 25 minutes.</div>\n<div class=\"arrow-right\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-arrow-right\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#arrow-right\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--steps-card paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<svg class=\"u-icon-trophy-flat-dims\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#trophy-flat\"></use>\n</svg>\n<div class=\"steps-label\">Sharpen Your Skills</div>\n<div>Celebrate adding to your skillset through courses and Micro-Certs.</div>\n<div class=\"arrow-right\">\n<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"u-icon-arrow-right\" role=\"presentation\">\n<use xlink:href=\"#arrow-right\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\"></use>\n</svg>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div class=\"has-bg-triangle container container--max-width u-padding-lg-bottom\">\n<div class=\"bg-triangle__container bg-triangle__container--no-mobile\">\n<svg class=\"bg-triangle__triangle bg-triangle__triangle--tab-menu-1\" viewbox=\"0 0 226 260\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M226 130.002L0 260V0l226 130.002z\" fill=\"#f3f2f3\"></path>\n</svg>\n<svg class=\"bg-triangle__triangle bg-triangle__triangle--tab-menu-2\" viewbox=\"0 0 226 260\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M226 130.002L0 260V0l226 130.002z\" fill=\"#f3f2f3\"></path>\n</svg>\n<svg class=\"bg-triangle__triangle bg-triangle__triangle--tab-menu-3\" viewbox=\"0 0 226 260\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M226 130.002L0 260V0l226 130.002z\" fill=\"#f3f2f3\"></path>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab tab-vertical\" id=\"tab-19485\">\n<div class=\"page-layout page-layout--2col\">\n<div class=\"container__grid container__grid--no-gap container__grid--2col\">\n<div class=\"tab-nav page-layout__col\" role=\"tablist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<a aria-controls=\"tab-19485-0\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"tab-link active\" data-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tab-19485-0\" id=\"tab-link-19485-0\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                  Micro-Certs\n                </a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a aria-controls=\"tab-19485-1\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"tab-link\" data-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tab-19485-1\" id=\"tab-link-19485-1\" role=\"tab\">\n                  Industry Specialization Courses\n                </a>\n</li>\n<li>\n<a aria-controls=\"tab-19485-2\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"tab-link\" data-toggle=\"tab\" href=\"#tab-19485-2\" id=\"tab-link-19485-2\" role=\"tab\">\n                  Agent &amp; Broker Focused Courses\n                </a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"tab-content page-layout__col\">\n<div aria-labelledby=\"tab-link-19485-0\" class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-19485-0\" role=\"tabpanel\">\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--tab paragraph--view-mode--full\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Explore the risk management and insurance industry, sharpen your skills, and advance your knowledge with <a href=\"/micro-certs\">Micro-Certs.</a> As you complete each Micro-Cert you will earn a digital badge to display in your email signature and social media profiles to showcase your expertise.</p><ul><li><a href=\"/managing-clients-cyber-risks\">Managing Clients’ Cyber Risks</a></li><li><a href=\"/leading-and-coaching-skills\">Leading and Coaching Skills</a></li><li><a href=\"/closing-commercial-coverage-gaps\">Closing Commercial Coverage Gaps</a></li><li><a href=\"/identifying-commercial-clients-risks\">Identifying Commercial Clients’ Risks</a></li><li><a href=\"/helping-clients-prepare-worst\">Helping Clients Prepare for the Worst</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-supplemental-personal-lines\">Understanding Supplemental Personal Lines</a></li><li><a href=\"/closing-business-income-coverage-gaps\">Closing Business Income Coverage Gaps</a></li><li><a href=\"/examining-workers-compensation-coverage\">Examining Workers Compensation Coverage</a></li><li><a href=\"/excelling-account-management\">Excelling at Account Management</a></li><li><a href=\"/exploring-todays-risk-management-and-insurance-landscape\">Exploring Today's Risk Management and Insurance Landscape</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-pc-ratemaking-and-pricing\">Understanding P&amp;C Ratemaking and Pricing</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-rmi-market-cycles\">Understanding RMI Market Cycles</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div aria-labelledby=\"tab-link-19485-1\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tab-19485-1\" role=\"tabpanel\">\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--tab paragraph--view-mode--full\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Discovery endless opportunity with <a href=\"/agents-and-brokers/market-specialization\">courses crafted to help you</a> better understand the nuances of risk management and insurance in specialized industries.</p><p>Select one course that focuses on your clients’ industry-specific risks and coverage gaps to become their trusted, consultative partner – or dive into multiple courses to find the industry that suits you best. </p><ul><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-construction-industry\">Construction</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-hospitality-industry\">Hospitality</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-real-estate-industry\">Real Estate</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-public-entities\">Public Entities</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-transportation-industry\">Transportation</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-manufacturing-industry\">Manufacturing</a></li><li><a href=\"/understanding-risks-healthcare-industry\">Healthcare</a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div aria-labelledby=\"tab-link-19485-2\" class=\"tab-pane\" id=\"tab-19485-2\" role=\"tabpanel\">\n<div class=\"paragraph paragraph--type--tab paragraph--view-mode--full\">\n<div class=\"container container--max-width paragraph paragraph--type--text paragraph--view-mode--default\">\n<div><p>Check out <a href=\"/agent-broker-online-courses\">short courses</a> targeted towards helping agents and brokers stay up to date on emerging trends and fundamentals.</p><ul><li><a href=\"/blockchain-in-insurance\"><span>Blockchain in Insurance</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/captive-insurance-fundamentals\"><span>Captive Insurance Fundamentals</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/cyber-risk-fundamentals\"><span>Cyber Risk Fundamentals</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/emerging-technologies-and-risk\"><span>Emerging Technologies and Risk</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/international-insurance-fundamentals\"><span>International Insurance Fundamentals</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/introduction-risk-management-and-insurance\"><span>Introduction to Risk Management and Insurance</span></a></li><li><a href=\"/successful-starts-csrs\">Successful Starts for CSRs</a></li><li><a href=\"/successful-starts-producers\"><span>Successful Starts for Producers</span></a></li></ul></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div><div class=\"container container--max-width u-padding-bottom\">\n<div class=\"u-text-center\">\n<h2>\n      Invest 25 minutes in your career today!\n    </h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</div></body></html>",
